+# Documentation & Onboarding — Review Report
+
+**Lane:** `documentation-and-onboarding`
+**Reviewer:** automated pipeline (human-triggable)
+**Date:** 2026-03-22
+
+---
+
+## Summary
+
+| Document | Pre-review Status | Post-review Status |
